# ── The boilerplate is a git repo that tracks ONLY its own shared config. ──
# Project repos live here as subfolders and stay their own independent git repos,
# so we ignore everything at the top level and re-include just the boilerplate's files.

/*
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/CLAUDE.md
!/package.json
!/bin/
!/templates/
!/knowledge/

# node (in case the boilerplate itself ever installs deps)
node_modules/

# OS / editor cruft (applies anywhere)
.DS_Store
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/
